<tableCitation id="CB708F91751DB7A7D17F00EED5F3265E" captionStart="Table 1" captionStartId="T1" captionText="Table 1. Measurements in mm: average + / - standard error (minimum-maximum) total abundance." httpUri="http://table.plazi.org/id/CFE4307320A4B6F615D3B13A128AAE39" pageId="0" pageNumber="83" tableUuid="CFE4307320A4B6F615D3B13A128AAE39">1</tableCitation>
). FWs very short, sometimes just visible under edge of pronotum (Fig. 
<figureCitation id="CF5394F7BE25644D505A94510F053476" captionStart="Fig. 4" captionStartId="F4" captionText="Fig. 4. Morphology of Neogryllopsis gorochovi sp. nov. A. Male head and pronotum; B. Male lateral view of head and pronotum; C. Male face; D. Female head, pronotum, and FWs; E. Male FW. Scale bars: 7 mm (A); 6 mm (B, E); 5 mm (C); 8 mm (D)." figureDoi="10.3897/jor.31.73389.fig4" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/690969" pageId="0" pageNumber="83">4D</figureCitation>
).
